### A call-and-response rhythm

```scheme
;; Call (loud, rhythmic)
(transport/tempo 105)
(note/place-at 1 'G3 'quarter 0.9)
(note/place-at 2 'G3 'eighth 0.85)
(note/place-at 2.5 'A3 'eighth 0.85)
(note/place-at 3 'G3 'quarter 0.9)

;; Response (softer, answering)
(note/place-at 5 'C4 'quarter 0.65)
(note/place-at 6 'B3 'quarter 0.65)
(note/place-at 7 'A3 'half 0.7)
```

