(note/strike 60 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 62 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 64 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 65 'quarter 64)

(base/land-on-downbeat)
(transport/tempo 110)
(note/strike 60 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 62 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 64 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 65 'quarter 64)

(base/land-on-downbeat)
(transport/tempo 100)
(note/strike 60 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 62 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 64 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 65 'quarter 64)

(base/land-on-downbeat)
(transport/tempo 90)
(note/strike 60 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 62 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 64 'quarter 64)
(note/strike 65 'quarter 64)
```

The tempo decreases from 120 to 110 to 100 to 90. The music slows.

`[VISUAL: Four 4/4 measures. Tempo markings: \"♩=120\", \"♩=110\", \"♩=100\", \"♩=90\".]`

